articles.title: Sick Kids reporting seven likely cases of severe acute hepatitis of unknown origin - Toronto Star
articles.description: Close to 300 cases of acute hepatitis of unknown origin have now been reported worldwide, including the U.S., South East Asia and many European countries, according to a BBC report.
articles.content:
